1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:35,009
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:39,410
[2000]

3
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:21,980
[Episode 34 The Two Sides of Life]

4
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,329
Alright.

5
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,170
Bride and groom, get ready.

6
00:02:33,170 --> 00:02:34,310
Look at the camera please.

7
00:02:34,310 --> 00:02:36,030
Alright. Three, two, one.

8
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:06,160
Zhenzhu.

9
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,150
Don't you think Xiaolan's wedding

10
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,240
is a bit too plain?

11
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:10,750
Though they're not doing

12
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:11,840
the traditional bowing ceremony,

13
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,080
they should at least, see—

14
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,680
add a touch of red
to make it festive, right?

15
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,520
Do the elders

16
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:17,750
from both sides
not have a problem with this?

17
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,560
Xiaolan told Cheng a long time ago

18
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,420
that she wanted a simple wedding.

19
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,120
Being surrounded by family and friends

20
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,650
is the greatest happiness.

21
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:27,560
Look, do Xiaolan's and Cheng's parents

22
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,190
seem displeased to you?

23
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:31,710
Sis Bai,

24
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,710
this wine

25
00:03:32,850 --> 00:03:34,370
is said to be from Gangdao.

26
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,020
It's very expensive.

27
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:35,420
Try it.

28
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:36,360
Here you are.

29
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:38,870
You are...

30
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,120
determined to be

31
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,920
on the bride's side then, right?

32
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,710
Of course.

33
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:43,680
When they got engaged,

34
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,480
I already said

35
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,680
that Xiaolan would be my sister

36
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:48,430
and Cheng my brother-in-law from then on.

37
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,030
You really

38
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,120
know when to act smart.

39
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,780
You'll achieve great things.

40
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,840
You Li, the two of you...

41
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,280
Sis Bai,

42
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,180
w-we're seeing how things go.

43
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:58,910
If we get married,

44
00:03:58,910 --> 00:04:00,240
we'll definitely let you know.

45
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:00,840
Okay.

46
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,430
Then I'll be waiting

47
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:02,760
for your wedding candy!

48
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,520
Cheers.

49
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:03,980
Cheers.

50
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,030
When they

51
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:09,210
first got together,

52
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:11,040
I hoped they'd get married soon.

53
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,760
But they were both too busy,

54
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,620
so I didn't want to pressure them.

55
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:16,269
Just let nature take its course.

56
00:04:16,269 --> 00:04:17,240
I used to be anxious too,

57
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,560
but now I've stopped rushing the kids.

58
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,160
She's just

59
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,920
so fond

60
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,680
of Xiaolan.

61
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:22,830
Granny Yu.

62
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,480
Let me take that.

63
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:24,950
Have some fruit.

64
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:25,800
Okay, hand it to me.

65
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,830
Granny Yu, would you like some?

66
00:04:26,830 --> 00:04:28,830
Hello, uncles, aunties, Granny Yu.

67
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,920
Today, I'm on the bride's side.

68
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:32,990
Granny Yu.

69
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,700
Do you enjoy this wedding?

70
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,830
Do you think a wedding

71
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,360
should be all red and bright

72
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,760
with bowing ceremonies?

73
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:41,190
Do I look like an old fogey to you?

74
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:42,530
Xiaolan and Zhou Cheng

75
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,870
want their wedding this way.

76
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,720
What they like matters most.

77
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,630
This wedding seems nice to me.

78
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,730
It's elegant

79
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,770
and natural.

80
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,010
Exactly.

81
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:53,630
Granny Yu

82
00:04:53,830 --> 00:04:55,000
has seen the world.

83
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:56,610
She's very open-minded.

84
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:59,159
I've long heard from Cheng

85
00:04:59,190 --> 00:05:01,050
about Granny Yu from Shengcheng.

86
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:03,840
Today, as I finally meet you,

87
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,260
I feel like we're already close.

88
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:06,860
We truly clicked right away.

89
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,390
Yes.

90
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,160
If possible,

91
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,750
we must gather and chat

92
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:10,480
more often.

93
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,270
-Sure.
-Right.

94
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:11,870
Sure thing.

95
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:13,360
When there's time, I'll take Granny Yu

96
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,560
to Jingcheng by plane.

97
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,510
No problem.

98
00:05:15,510 --> 00:05:17,120
When you get to Jingcheng,
I'll treat you to

99
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,480
the best hotpot in the city.

100
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,340
Eateries, too.

101
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,160
Look, there they are.

102
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,240
Hello, Granny Yu.

103
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:23,070
We're here.

104
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,680
Hello, Auntie.

105
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,800
Hello, Auntie.

106
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,320
Hello, Mr. Zhou and Mrs. Zhou.

107
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,380
Hello, Mayor Tang.

108
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:30,630
Look,

109
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:31,510
over these years,

110
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:32,630
Xiaolan has always exposed us

111
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:34,030
to all sorts of new stuff.

112
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,040
Such a beautifully decorated venue,

113
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,560
see?

114
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:37,950
All is like a dream,

115
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,190
or a movie scene.

116
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:39,920
Isn't it?

117
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,720
Xiaolan

118
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:41,870
always

119
00:05:41,870 --> 00:05:43,320
brings us surprises.

120
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:44,190
That's right.

121
00:05:44,409 --> 00:05:44,940
She does.

122
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,150
Here comes the bride!

123
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,380
-Here she is!
-Here she is!

124
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,270
You're gorgeous!

125
00:06:08,630 --> 00:06:10,120
Let's welcome the groom!

126
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,560
-So handsome!
-Bravo!

127
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,830
Why don't they

128
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:32,310
walk down the aisle together?

129
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:34,110
Isn't it bad to do it separately?

130
00:06:34,190 --> 00:06:35,060
It's a tradition

131
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:37,360
for the bride to make an entrance
with her father.

132
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,510
But now, Xiaolan has asked

133
00:06:38,510 --> 00:06:40,240
her mother to walk her down

134
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:41,680
the aisle.

135
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:42,190
Go ahead.

136
00:06:42,190 --> 00:06:42,870
Hurry, go quickly.

137
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:43,409
I'm going then.

138
00:06:43,409 --> 00:06:44,010
Off you go.

139
00:06:48,430 --> 00:06:49,600
Who made that wedding dress?

140
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,460
It's stunning.

141
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:51,560
Chen.

142
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,600
Teresa, why would you come?

143
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:55,270
It's just been one month, right?

144
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:56,310
I thought I must attend

145
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:57,440
Xiaolan's wedding.

146
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,040
Chen,

147
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,670
you really put your heart

148
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,680
into making this wedding dress.

149
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,070
I certainly had to help Xia hold

150
00:07:02,070 --> 00:07:04,000
the most beautiful wedding of all.

151
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:06,870
Mom.

152
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:07,890
Xiaolan.

153
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,730
Are you nervous?

154
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:12,310
No, I'm not.

155
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,240
I know

156
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:15,880
that your days ahead

157
00:07:16,230 --> 00:07:18,090
will be filled with abundant joy.

158
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,270
The wedding will commence soon.

159
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:28,190
Dear guests, please take your seats.

160
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:28,720
Let's go.

161
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:29,160
This way.

162
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:29,830
Move along, please.

163
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:30,290
Thanks.

164
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:39,740
♪ Maybe all encounters in the world ♪

165
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:44,230
♪ Are predetermined by destiny ♪

166
00:07:45,990 --> 00:07:50,950
♪ The opening and closing chapters
are written ♪

167
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:54,990
♪ From when we first met ♪

168
00:07:55,659 --> 00:07:59,490
♪ Till now, though much has changed ♪

169
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:06,640
♪ Our hearts remain unchanged ♪

170
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:12,330
♪ Making a dream in your eyes ♪

171
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:22,500
♪ Time passes by,
yet I still love you the same ♪

172
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:28,010
♪ After traveling through the crowds
and dark tides ♪

173
00:08:28,620 --> 00:08:37,780
♪ We must embrace
with the weight of the moment ♪

174
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:42,409
♪ If a short hug is all we can have ♪

175
00:08:42,770 --> 00:08:46,440
♪ As a challenge of fate ♪

176
00:08:49,130 --> 00:08:53,730
♪ I don't want you to have any regrets ♪

177
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:50,890
Xiaolan,

178
00:08:51,550 --> 00:08:52,210
Zhou Cheng,

179
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,910
I send you my best wishes.

180
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,510
I hope the two of you will strive together

181
00:08:54,890 --> 00:08:57,830
♪ Let's break the barriers
of time and space ♪

182
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,720
for progress,

183
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:58,790
and be happy ever after.

184
00:08:58,340 --> 00:09:02,080
♪ However ridiculous or bizarre
things are ♪

185
00:09:04,770 --> 00:09:09,930
♪ I'm determined to stick with you ♪

186
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,720
Auntie...

187
00:09:10,250 --> 00:09:15,530
♪ Making a dream in your eyes ♪

188
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:13,510
Mom,

189
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,880
rest assured.

190
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,230
We will.

191
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:25,760
♪ A smile of yours
holds my life in its way ♪

192
00:09:26,050 --> 00:09:31,050
♪ Traveling through time and space,
courage is all I have ♪

193
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:30,720
Now, bride and groom,
please exchange rings.

194
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:43,850
♪ I hope you'll understand
how my heart flips for you ♪

195
00:09:57,430 --> 00:10:00,960
♪ If a short hug is all we can have ♪

196
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,480
Bravo!

197
00:10:01,590 --> 00:10:05,540
♪ As a challenge of fate ♪

198
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:20,080
-Kiss each other!
-Kiss!

199
00:10:07,830 --> 00:10:12,740
♪ I don't want you to have any regrets ♪

200
00:10:13,190 --> 00:10:16,740
♪ Let's break the barriers
of time and space ♪

201
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:21,130
♪ However ridiculous or bizarre
things are ♪

202
00:10:23,140 --> 00:10:28,130
♪ I'm determined to stick with you ♪

203
00:10:29,030 --> 00:10:33,980
♪ Making a dream in your eyes ♪

204
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:43,860
♪ A smile of yours
holds my life in its way ♪

205
00:10:44,810 --> 00:10:49,700
♪ Traveling through time and space,
courage is all I have ♪

206
00:10:50,250 --> 00:11:02,490
♪ I hope you'll understand
how my heart flips for you ♪

207
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:20,760
♪ All my beloved ones are around ♪

208
00:11:21,570 --> 00:11:24,910
♪ Right at this moment ♪

209
00:11:25,470 --> 00:11:29,460
♪ Happiness is clearly visible ♪

210
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:36,460
♪ Holding hands,
we walk in a rain of petals ♪

211
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:44,390
♪ Let's raise the glasses
filled with champagne and blessings ♪

212
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:48,540
♪ Thank you for being with me ♪

213
00:11:49,290 --> 00:11:53,970
♪ And completing my life ♪

214
00:11:54,510 --> 00:12:00,640
♪ For my love, dance in the wind ♪

215
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,550
In my previous life

216
00:11:58,750 --> 00:11:59,600
and this life,

217
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,550
the best thing

218
00:12:01,190 --> 00:12:09,020
♪ The world blooms at your feet ♪

219
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:04,200
that I could imagine

220
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,260
doesn't get better than this.

221
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:10,510
In the building of my own creation,

222
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:16,660
♪ Let there be embraces;
smiles and tears are priceless ♪

223
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:11,940
those who I love

224
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,730
and those who love me are all around me.

225
00:12:17,130 --> 00:12:21,620
♪ Life is beautiful like a painting ♪

226
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:18,600
Each of them is happy,

227
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:20,600
and they're happy about

228
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,480
me being happy at the same time.

229
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:27,820
♪ Keep going;
happiness is all that matters ♪

230
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,290
What I've always wanted

231
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:27,720
and yearned for

232
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,510
is a scene like this.

233
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:48,150
♪ Shining heart,
let joy dissolve into the air ♪

234
00:12:48,540 --> 00:12:52,900
♪ Let our hearts roam in the sky ♪

235
00:12:54,120 --> 00:13:00,840
♪ Sway and dance,
with your heart toward the sun ♪

236
00:13:21,530 --> 00:13:25,930
[Gangdao]

237
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:45,600
Are you sneaking around

238
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,060
to try to scare me to death?

239
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,840
Do you have friends in the mansion?

240
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:50,670
Go ask them for me

241
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:52,200
if the Master has returned.

242
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:53,030
Yes.

243
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,240
What a lousy maid.

244
00:14:11,330 --> 00:14:12,360
I'm telling you, guys,

245
00:14:12,360 --> 00:14:13,480
I've never been to a wedding

246
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:15,030
as special as yours.

247
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,790
I had so much fun.

248
00:14:16,890 --> 00:14:18,460
See, the wine was good,

249
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:20,010
and there was dancing.

250
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:22,140
The two of you danced so beautifully.

251
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,390
Granny Yu, if you like it,

252
00:14:23,390 --> 00:14:24,510
we'll hold a wedding

253
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:25,770
every day. How about that?

254
00:14:25,770 --> 00:14:26,230
I agree.

255
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:32,270
After the wedding,

256
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:34,640
a-are the two of you moving to my place?

257
00:14:35,510 --> 00:14:35,960
Yes.

258
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:39,100
Then what about your place
at the Golden Sands Pool?

259
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:40,720
Our place at the Golden Sands Pool

260
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,080
is still under renovation.

261
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,680
Granny Yu,

262
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,240
I saved an apartment for you

263
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,320
right downstairs from ours.

264
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:46,290
In the future, you can stay there

265
00:14:46,290 --> 00:14:48,150
or at your old place as you please.

266
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:55,820
Granny Yu, what's wrong?

267
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:56,570
Easy, easy.

268
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:58,000
Granny Yu, are you carsick?

269
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,060
Shall we pull over?

270
00:15:00,910 --> 00:15:02,110
I'm not feeling well.

271
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:03,840
Ge Jian, go to the hospital.

272
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,670
Hurry, to the hospital.

273
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:05,400
Okay, got it.

274
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,600
Granny Yu!

275
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,630
Please wait outside!

276
00:15:26,510 --> 00:15:26,960
Mom?

277
00:15:27,630 --> 00:15:28,290
Uncle Tang?

278
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,670
Why are you here?

279
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,550
I'm feeling terrible.

280
00:15:32,550 --> 00:15:34,270
We've thrown up several times.

281
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,600
I can't take it anymore.

282
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:39,040
Given our tolerance for alcohol,
we shouldn't be like this.

283
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:41,270
We didn't reach our limits yet.

284
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:42,170
Liu Fen, Tang Hong'en,

285
00:15:42,170 --> 00:15:42,870
come with me.

286
00:15:42,870 --> 00:15:43,440
Let's go.

287
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,840
-Come on.
-Go over there.

288
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,840
Don't worry. We'll just be in there.

289
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,300
Call the police, Xiaolan.

290
00:15:59,790 --> 00:16:01,080
Ms. Zhang, are you okay?

291
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:01,870
I'm fine.

292
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:18,030
[Gangdao]

293
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:19,790
Quiet down!

294
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,650
Do not obstruct our duties!

295
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:24,550
Fine.

296
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:25,200
Yes.

297
00:16:27,790 --> 00:16:29,720
Master!

298
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,360
How do we cope without you?

299
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,670
What should we do?

300
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:39,360
Stop crying!

301
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:41,190
You're in a hospital now,

302
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,320
not a market.

303
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:43,630
Watch the kids!

304
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,370
Why did you bring them here?

305
00:16:45,550 --> 00:16:47,410
Is this even a place for children?

306
00:16:47,630 --> 00:16:48,510
All that crying and howling...

307
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:50,510
Are you putting on a show for others?

308
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:54,790
Excuse me.

309
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:56,150
How is Mr. Du?

310
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:58,270
We are still resuscitating the patient.

311
00:16:58,270 --> 00:16:59,200
Can you please stop making

312
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,000
so much noise?

313
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,720
I'm sorry for that.

314
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:02,800
Just keep quiet.

315
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:04,530
Don't disrupt our work.

316
00:17:04,790 --> 00:17:05,589
My apologies.

317
00:17:05,750 --> 00:17:06,480
I'm so sorry.

318
00:17:06,790 --> 00:17:07,720
Please save him!

319
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:10,510
Did you hear that?

320
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:11,609
Stop making noise!

321
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,760
You're such a disgrace.

322
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:13,420
Go sit down!

323
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:17,609
You all are such a pain in the neck.

324
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:35,740
Inside, your husband's life is at stake.

325
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:38,400
Outside, your son is still missing.

326
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:39,890
Auntie Song,

327
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:42,200
take good care of yourself.

328
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:46,810
This is a hospital.

329
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:48,570
Why make so much noise?

330
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,790
Do you want everyone to think

331
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:51,790
that we the Du family all have

332
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:52,590
poor manners?

333
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:55,110
Then what can we do now?

334
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,200
What do you want to do?

335
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,010
Mr. Du...

336
00:18:01,230 --> 00:18:02,070
How is Mr. Du?

337
00:18:02,270 --> 00:18:02,720
Mr. Du.

338
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:03,560
Mr. Du!

339
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:04,410
How is Mr. Du?

340
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:06,360
Tell me. How is Mr. Du doing now?

341
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:07,680
-Miss, calm down.
-Say something!

342
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:08,160
Mr. Du!

343
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:08,970
Mr. Du...

344
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:10,110
Enough!

345
00:18:10,290 --> 00:18:11,830
We just got a complaint about us.

346
00:18:11,830 --> 00:18:13,590
The doctor also told us
not to make any noise.

347
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:15,250
Mr. Du is being resuscitated!

348
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:21,470
I can't bear to watch you.

349
00:18:28,510 --> 00:18:30,370
It's not time for you to mourn yet.

350
00:18:59,030 --> 00:18:59,560
Xiaolan.

351
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:20,350
Mom and Uncle Tang have gone home.

352
00:19:20,350 --> 00:19:21,440
The doctor has prescribed medicine
for them.

353
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:22,570
They should be fine.

354
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:24,400
San and Wei are in more serious condition.

355
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:25,920
They're getting IVs
at the No. 2 Hospital.

356
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:26,980
I've asked around.

357
00:19:27,450 --> 00:19:29,450
The older guests are actually fine.

358
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,350
The doctor suspects

359
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:32,010
this is a food poisoning case.

360
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:33,840
Xiaolan,

361
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,920
are you feeling unwell?

362
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:39,940
It was the red wine.

363
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:42,720
Older people

364
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,520
usually don't like red wine,

365
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:46,540
so they're showing less or no symptoms.

366
00:19:46,540 --> 00:19:48,080
Granny Yu has
pre-existing medical conditions,

367
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:49,940
so she's having a worse reaction.

368
00:19:52,030 --> 00:19:52,440
Hello.

369
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:54,010
Who called the police?

370
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:56,350
Me, I did.

371
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:57,830
I suspect

372
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:58,920
someone poisoned

373
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:00,250
our wedding reception.

374
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:10,130
Here is a copy of the purchase list.

375
00:20:10,170 --> 00:20:11,440
The items were procured
by different people

376
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,770
from different places.

377
00:20:13,290 --> 00:20:14,350
Okay. Please stick around

378
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:15,590
to assist with our investigation.

379
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:16,520
Got it, officer.

380
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:19,000
Take this list and look into it.

381
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:19,970
Yes, sir.

382
00:20:23,070 --> 00:20:24,930
How is the situation at the venue?

383
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,420
Ms. Xia,

384
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:26,920
the police arrived quickly.

385
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:28,050
The food at the venue

386
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:29,440
hasn't been cleared yet.

387
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:31,350
Samples are being taken of every dish.

388
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:32,470
Whether this is food poisoning

389
00:20:32,470 --> 00:20:33,790
or intentional poisoning,

390
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:35,450
there should be results soon.

391
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:38,440
What about those who procured the things?

392
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,000
I'm having them stay temporarily

393
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,310
in the company dormitory.

394
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:41,680
Okay.

395
00:20:42,160 --> 00:20:42,920
Tell them

396
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,880
it's not that we don't trust them.

397
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,550
This just has to be done
as so to assist the police

398
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:47,950
with the investigation.

399
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:49,400
They're all showing great understanding

400
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,510
and hoping the root cause can be found

401
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:51,640
as soon as possible.

402
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:52,810
Thank you, Ge Jian.

403
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:54,760
Keep me posted

404
00:20:54,790 --> 00:20:55,680
on any updates.

405
00:20:56,290 --> 00:20:57,090
Sure, Ms. Xia.

406
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:06,360
Get some rest.

407
00:21:14,210 --> 00:21:15,670
Take a nap if you're tired.

408
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:16,760
I'm here for you.

409
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,080
Don't worry.

410
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:52,850
Anything wrong?

411
00:21:53,550 --> 00:21:54,950
Did you have a nightmare?

412
00:21:59,310 --> 00:22:00,910
Yes. But by the time I woke up,

413
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:03,280
I had forgotten everything.

414
00:22:04,830 --> 00:22:06,360
That said, I still remember

415
00:22:07,110 --> 00:22:08,440
that feeling of loss...

416
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:11,350
and fear.

417
00:22:15,790 --> 00:22:17,790
Dreams are the opposite of reality.

418
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:18,930
Don't worry.

419
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:21,780
They just brought some food over.

420
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:22,690
Grab a bite.

421
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:24,830
I know

422
00:22:25,510 --> 00:22:26,070
you won't listen to me

423
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:27,800
even if I tell you to go home now.

424
00:22:27,830 --> 00:22:28,890
Then just stay here

425
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,600
and keep Granny Yu company.

426
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:31,950
If anything comes up,

427
00:22:32,150 --> 00:22:33,910
Ge Jian and others will take care of it.

428
00:22:33,910 --> 00:22:34,910
Just don't worry.

429
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,510
Being surrounded

430
00:22:40,440 --> 00:22:41,350
by family,

431
00:22:42,550 --> 00:22:44,010
friends, and the man I love

432
00:22:44,650 --> 00:22:45,450
feels so good.

433
00:22:49,070 --> 00:22:49,960
Zhou Cheng,

434
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:52,440
I'm a very greedy.

435
00:22:53,580 --> 00:22:55,510
I don't want to lose what I have now.

436
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,330
We are all there for you.

437
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:01,680
We'll always be.

438
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:04,360
You won't lose anything.

439
00:23:05,510 --> 00:23:06,310
Rest assured.

440
00:23:14,210 --> 00:23:18,280
[Gangdao]

441
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,600
How is the Master today?

442
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:33,590
I'm asking you

443
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:35,250
how the Master is doing today!

444
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,160
Vivi!

445
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:43,770
How is the Master doing?

446
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:46,310
He drowned,

447
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:46,880
and...

448
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:48,880
his head got injured.

449
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:50,550
The doctor said...

450
00:23:53,030 --> 00:23:55,030
Can't you finish it before crying?

451
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:56,810
The doctor said...

452
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,880
he might never wake up...

453
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,880
and be in a coma forever.

454
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:20,200
Mr. Cheng,

455
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:22,270
nobody knows when my old man

456
00:24:22,270 --> 00:24:23,400
will wake up.

457
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:25,750
Now, the Du family is left leaderless

458
00:24:25,750 --> 00:24:26,610
in sheer chaos.

459
00:24:27,510 --> 00:24:28,640
Did my old man devise

460
00:24:29,270 --> 00:24:30,160
any contingency plans

461
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,620
for a situation like this?

462
00:24:33,210 --> 00:24:34,000
Mr. Du did have

463
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,600
a power of attorney written.

464
00:24:37,270 --> 00:24:38,960
Should he get into an accident

465
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,920
and become unable to personally handle

466
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,050
corporate affairs,

467
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:43,570
whoever in the Du family

468
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:44,880
holds shares

469
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:45,920
of the group

470
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:48,110
will be given the power

471
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:49,840
to temporarily act in his role.

472
00:24:51,730 --> 00:24:53,990
When was this power of attorney written?

473
00:24:59,310 --> 00:25:00,030
Mr. Cheng,

474
00:25:01,550 --> 00:25:02,880
if I hadn't asked today,

475
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:05,260
would you have ever brought it up?

476
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:06,350
Would you just watch

477
00:25:06,350 --> 00:25:08,150
our stock price keep plummeting

478
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,530
and not do anything?

479
00:25:10,070 --> 00:25:10,870
Young Master,

480
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:13,720
me keeping it secret

481
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:15,580
is a term of the power of attorney.

482
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:18,110
Let me venture a guess.

483
00:25:18,510 --> 00:25:19,400
Mr. Du probably

484
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:21,000
had concerns about

485
00:25:21,510 --> 00:25:22,640
leaving the company

486
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,070
under the charge of a family member

487
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:25,640
who has never showed care

488
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,770
for its operations.

489
00:25:27,200 --> 00:25:28,400
Do attorneys like you

490
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,350
all speak

491
00:25:29,350 --> 00:25:30,610
in such an obscure way?

492
00:25:31,870 --> 00:25:32,730
How about this?

493
00:25:33,110 --> 00:25:34,710
Let me ask you in another way.

494
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:36,200
Now that Du Zhaoji

495
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:37,550
has ruthlessly

496
00:25:37,550 --> 00:25:38,590
targeted his own father...

497
00:25:38,590 --> 00:25:39,390
Young Master,

498
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:41,050
there is no proof of it yet.

499
00:25:41,050 --> 00:25:42,580
He has fled. Isn't it proof?

500
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:50,110
I've worked for Mr. Du for many years.

501
00:25:50,830 --> 00:25:53,110
Professionally and personally,

502
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:55,000
my advice to you is

503
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:57,070
that you should focus on

504
00:25:57,350 --> 00:25:59,590
how to stabilize the group

505
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:02,750
in the shortest time possible.

506
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:05,560
As for the other matters,

507
00:26:06,030 --> 00:26:07,590
Mr. Du will attend to them himself

508
00:26:07,590 --> 00:26:08,750
when he wakes up.

509
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:12,110
Even if he can't wake up,

510
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:14,100
you should turn to the police.

511
00:26:16,070 --> 00:26:16,730
Certainly,

512
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:17,760
Young Master,

513
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:19,070
it's just a piece of advice

514
00:26:19,070 --> 00:26:19,720
from me.

515
00:26:20,750 --> 00:26:22,440
Since I'm being paid by the Du family,

516
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:24,640
of course I would look out for all of you.

517
00:26:25,790 --> 00:26:27,150
Getting the company in order

518
00:26:27,150 --> 00:26:28,630
is the priority right now.

519
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:34,110
Mr. Cheng,

520
00:26:35,550 --> 00:26:37,950
no wonder my old man
thinks so highly of you.

521
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:39,400
You can do

522
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:40,720
more than

523
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:42,610
just an ordinary attorney's job.

524
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,000
Young Master,

525
00:26:44,510 --> 00:26:46,370
if you take charge of the company,

526
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,600
I'll naturally work for you.

527
00:26:53,110 --> 00:26:54,680
This concludes the reading

528
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:57,160
of Mr. Du Chengrong's power of attorney.

529
00:26:57,160 --> 00:26:58,760
According to this document,

530
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:01,510
currently, only Mr. Du Zhaohui

531
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:03,100
holds shares of the group,

532
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:04,070
so

533
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:05,680
from today on,

534
00:27:06,350 --> 00:27:08,150
Mr. Du Zhaohui will temporarily

535
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:10,490
serve as the acting chairman of the group.

536
00:27:15,510 --> 00:27:16,550
When was this power of attorney

537
00:27:16,550 --> 00:27:17,270
signed?

538
00:27:17,790 --> 00:27:18,550
Why did I never hear

539
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:19,960
Chairman Du talk about it?

540
00:27:19,960 --> 00:27:21,220
Mr. Cao, are you saying

541
00:27:21,440 --> 00:27:23,750
that Chairman Du should
ask for your opinion

542
00:27:23,750 --> 00:27:25,480
every time he signs a document?

543
00:27:26,030 --> 00:27:26,560
Mr. Meng,

544
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:28,730
what do you mean by that?

545
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:30,360
I just asked you a question.

546
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:32,400
Or rather,

547
00:27:33,270 --> 00:27:35,240
do you not trust Mr. Cheng?

548
00:27:36,790 --> 00:27:39,450
The group will be taken over
by the Young Master.

549
00:27:47,590 --> 00:27:48,200
Everyone.

550
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:51,160
I have lots of things to do

551
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,790
both in the group and the hospital.

552
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:53,510
I really can't spend

553
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:54,840
more time with you here.

554
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,030
If any of you

555
00:27:57,350 --> 00:27:59,000
have doubts about this power of attorney

556
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,310
or what Mr. Cheng said,

557
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:05,310
go have your eyes

558
00:28:05,550 --> 00:28:06,950
and brains checked then.

559
00:28:18,750 --> 00:28:19,160
Okay.

560
00:28:21,270 --> 00:28:21,800
Alright.

561
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:22,750
Got it.

562
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:28,310
Your guess was correct.

563
00:28:28,310 --> 00:28:30,240
The problem did lie in the red wine.

564
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:31,680
What about the food?

565
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,440
Nothing wrong has been found

566
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,480
about the food yet.

567
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,540
Ge Jian just told me

568
00:28:35,750 --> 00:28:36,750
he had traced the winery

569
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:38,200
that produced the red wine.

570
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:39,730
It belongs to the Du family.

571
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,240
The Du family?

572
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:43,110
Ms. Xia!

573
00:28:43,510 --> 00:28:44,480
Someone delivered a letter

574
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,640
and said it must be handed to you.

575
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:48,040
He then left without saying anything else.

576
00:28:59,890 --> 00:29:00,950
It's Ye Xiaoqiong.

577
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:06,720
Ms. Xia,

578
00:29:07,510 --> 00:29:09,440
by the time you receive this letter,

579
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,970
I will have taken my revenge

580
00:29:11,480 --> 00:29:13,640
and left Gangdao already.

581
00:29:16,660 --> 00:29:17,780
Du Zhaohui has decided go straight

582
00:29:17,780 --> 00:29:19,510
and start a legitimate business?

583
00:29:19,510 --> 00:29:20,570
Then what about me?

584
00:29:21,090 --> 00:29:22,440
Am I supposed to rely on his charity

585
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:23,240
in the future?

586
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:25,280
Doesn't he like that woman?

587
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:27,280
Why didn't he go to her wedding?

588
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:29,590
They should've died together!

589
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:30,350
Second Young Master...

590
00:29:30,350 --> 00:29:31,370
Go away!

591
00:29:40,440 --> 00:29:41,240
Two days ago,

592
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:42,840
a call was made to the office.

593
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:45,000
Hearing about Du Zhaoji's absence,

594
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:46,400
the caller was panicked.

595
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:48,170
Before the call was hung up,

596
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:49,350
I heard them saying

597
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:50,930
Vivi was out of contact too.

598
00:29:51,110 --> 00:29:54,240
I think that caller was probably
a staffer of the winery.

599
00:29:54,590 --> 00:29:55,240
I'm not sure

600
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:56,640
if this is helpful to you,

601
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,110
but there is nothing more

602
00:29:58,110 --> 00:29:59,240
I can do for you.

603
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:01,640
Now,

604
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:03,200
I'm off to seek out

605
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,350
my next haven.

606
00:30:05,120 --> 00:30:07,450
I hope when we see each other again
one day,

607
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,570
I'll still be the same Ye Xiaoqiong

608
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:11,290
that you first met.

609
00:30:14,240 --> 00:30:14,900
Xiaoqiong,

610
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:17,870
I'm sure you'll find your own path.

611
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:26,640
Old Man,

612
00:30:27,830 --> 00:30:28,960
I've come to see you.

613
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:30,930
Look at you,

614
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:33,210
having so many women and sons.

615
00:30:33,720 --> 00:30:35,920
But once the power of attorney was read,

616
00:30:35,920 --> 00:30:37,050
they all scattered.

617
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:39,810
At the end of the day,

618
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,970
nobody but me came to visit you.

619
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:44,650
Don't get me wrong.

620
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:46,000
I'm not doing this because I am

621
00:30:46,000 --> 00:30:47,530
more loyal than the others.

622
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,680
I've benefited from you, after all.

623
00:30:50,310 --> 00:30:52,160
I just have to play the part

624
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,830
of a filial son.

625
00:31:04,750 --> 00:31:06,550
You deserve such suffering.

626
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,090
You've had your fun.

627
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,160
However,

628
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:13,370
have you ever thought about us?

629
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:14,240
Have you ever

630
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,440
truly cared about us?

631
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:18,550
How much do you

632
00:31:18,550 --> 00:31:20,280
actually know about our lives?

633
00:31:20,590 --> 00:31:21,110
For example,

634
00:31:21,110 --> 00:31:22,400
during the party

635
00:31:22,750 --> 00:31:23,950
for my 18th birthday,

636
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,590
somebody boldly slipped drugs in my drink.

637
00:31:26,590 --> 00:31:28,320
I was nearly poisoned to death.

638
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,790
Do you even know about

639
00:31:31,480 --> 00:31:33,080
that special birthday gift?

640
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:35,750
Another incident

641
00:31:35,750 --> 00:31:37,550
happened when I was 19 years old.

642
00:31:37,750 --> 00:31:39,350
I had a drag race with others,

643
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:42,110
and someone tampered with the brakes.

644
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:42,480
No.

645
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:46,610
Let me tell you a more recent incident.

646
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:48,200
When I turned 24, I meant

647
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,600
to do something serious.

648
00:31:50,310 --> 00:31:52,910
So I went with others to a pier
to inspect goods.

649
00:31:54,030 --> 00:31:57,030
Then suddenly,
I got caught in a gang fight

650
00:31:57,790 --> 00:32:00,270
and was nearly killed in the crossfire.

651
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,350
I'm so lucky and blessed
to be able to sit here

652
00:32:03,350 --> 00:32:04,920
and talk to you today.

653
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:07,030
Do you have any idea

654
00:32:07,310 --> 00:32:09,200
how many times I've been targeted?

655
00:32:09,200 --> 00:32:10,400
I'm not stupid.

656
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:14,590
I know you're aware of
each assassination attempt

657
00:32:14,590 --> 00:32:15,720
against me.

658
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:20,640
In fact, I owe you thanks.

659
00:32:23,510 --> 00:32:24,910
I know you kept testing me

660
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:27,750
to see if I had the ability

661
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,730
to take over the Du family.

662
00:32:30,550 --> 00:32:32,480
That actually made me stop caring.

663
00:32:33,110 --> 00:32:34,240
And because of that,

664
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:35,990
I luckily escaped danger

665
00:32:36,400 --> 00:32:37,350
multiple times.

666
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:47,350
Old Man,

667
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,510
what exactly happened?

668
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:55,010
How did you get yourself into this state?

669
00:33:09,440 --> 00:33:09,840
Hello?

670
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,300
Du Zhaohui,

671
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:13,350
your dad's still alive, right?

672
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:14,070
Where is

673
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:15,000
Xia Ziyu?

674
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:16,760
Xia Ziyu is now

675
00:33:17,160 --> 00:33:18,090
in the hospital.

676
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:19,610
She comes by every day,

677
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:21,800
cries and puts on an act,

678
00:33:21,830 --> 00:33:23,880
trying to wake my comatose father.

679
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:25,400
Pretending to show care

680
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,330
for a man who might never wake up...

681
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,640
I guess...

682
00:33:29,270 --> 00:33:30,750
for Xia Ziyu,

683
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,000
the ICU

684
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:33,310
is the safest place.

685
00:33:34,030 --> 00:33:34,480
Why?

686
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:35,750
Do you also think she is

687
00:33:35,750 --> 00:33:37,080
related to this matter?

688
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:38,920
I already told the police

689
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,200
this must be the conspiracy

690
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,200
of her and Brat Ji.

691
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:42,850
But the police said

692
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:43,640
they couldn't arrest them

693
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,790
due to lack of evidence.

694
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:46,790
I don't care about
the Du family's affairs.

695
00:33:46,790 --> 00:33:48,050
The only thing I'm sure

696
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:50,570
is that Xia Ziyu must be the one who hurt

697
00:33:51,310 --> 00:33:52,570
my family and friends.

698
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,110
Ms. Xia,

699
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:56,740
don't forget she was driven crazy by you.

700
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:58,240
She would've

701
00:33:59,310 --> 00:34:00,840
gone crazy even without me.

702
00:34:04,030 --> 00:34:06,160
Whether Du Chengrong will come to or not,

703
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:06,750
the Du family

704
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:08,210
is bound to get into a mess.

705
00:34:09,190 --> 00:34:09,790
By the way,

706
00:34:10,070 --> 00:34:11,130
how did your old man

707
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:12,280
get injured?

708
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,810
The only thing I know
is that he was on the way

709
00:34:14,810 --> 00:34:16,540
to acquire an antique that day.

710
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:25,449
Why did you take this route?

711
00:34:26,429 --> 00:34:27,840
Traffic gets heavy on rainy days.

712
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,639
This route can save us some time.

713
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,090
Such terrible weather.

714
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,760
How about we ask Mr. Qiu to postpone

715
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:35,489
the meeting?

716
00:34:36,110 --> 00:34:36,710
Master,

717
00:34:37,230 --> 00:34:38,360
we're almost there.

718
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,260
In such a hurry?

719
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:59,840
Are you afraid
that I'd pull the plug on him?

720
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,570
Don't worry.

721
00:35:01,110 --> 00:35:02,440
A brother of mine already

722
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,440
made an attempt to kill our father.

723
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:04,170
It's enough.

724
00:35:36,710 --> 00:35:37,970
Granny Yu needs to stay

725
00:35:38,230 --> 00:35:40,890
a few more days in the hospital
for observation.

726
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:43,040
I underestimated my enemy.

727
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:45,920
Never did it occur to me

728
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:48,070
that she'd target my family

729
00:35:48,070 --> 00:35:48,920
and friends.

730
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:53,030
When I first

731
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,230
woke up

732
00:35:55,230 --> 00:35:56,490
in Xia Xiaolan's body,

733
00:35:57,230 --> 00:35:58,760
in front of me
was a group of Xia family members

734
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:00,400
who wished I would die soon.

735
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:04,200
I confronted them bravely at that time.

736
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:07,030
In the time and space

737
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:08,400
where I used to be,

738
00:36:08,880 --> 00:36:09,880
I already grew accustomed

739
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:11,940
to being indifferent to everything.

740
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:15,480
Only on that day

741
00:36:16,230 --> 00:36:17,110
did I realize

742
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:19,620
that venting anger

743
00:36:20,510 --> 00:36:21,240
felt so good.

744
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:24,440
Why don't you just go die?

745
00:36:25,230 --> 00:36:27,070
Protecting her now, aren't you?

746
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,600
You terrible old hag,

747
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:31,710
watching your mouth

748
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:32,960
would be the only good deed
you can do for yourself.

749
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,480
She's calling me a terrible old hag.

750
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:35,440
Xiaolan, what are you saying?

751
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:36,440
Is this Xia household

752
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:38,000
too small for you now?

753
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:39,480
Yeah, this lousy place

754
00:36:39,590 --> 00:36:41,650
really can't handle someone like me.

755
00:36:44,230 --> 00:36:44,840
At that time,

756
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:46,840
it was my mom who gave me the courage.

757
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:50,880
Gradually,

758
00:36:51,680 --> 00:36:53,140
I didn't just protect her.

759
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:56,360
I actually began to love her.

760
00:36:57,880 --> 00:36:58,960
Later on,

761
00:37:00,670 --> 00:37:01,730
you guys showed up.

762
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:05,660
Zhou Cheng,

763
00:37:08,590 --> 00:37:10,110
if I own everything

764
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:11,840
but the power

765
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,500
to protect those I care about,

766
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:16,710
what will be the point of having so much?

767
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,000
I've forgotten and become unable

768
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,000
to recall clearly

769
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:24,610
many things from the past.

770
00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:28,200
But I still remember the feeling

771
00:37:29,230 --> 00:37:30,960
of being lonely and helpless.

772
00:37:32,710 --> 00:37:34,440
I am the brave person I am now

773
00:37:37,710 --> 00:37:38,920
because of all of you.

774
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:41,720
Xiaolan,

775
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:44,710
love is mutual.

776
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,730
Everyone loves you

777
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:49,550
and feels the love

778
00:37:49,550 --> 00:37:50,510
you give away.

779
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:52,540
Therefore,

780
00:37:58,230 --> 00:37:59,760
don't feel burdened at all.

781
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,860
Lately, I've been feeling

782
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:08,210
that something is about to happen.

783
00:38:09,670 --> 00:38:10,320
If...

784
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:13,160
I mean, hypothetically,

785
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:15,970
-if this matter...
-Don't worry.

786
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,730
No matter what happens,

787
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:20,160
I'll be there for you.

788
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:25,250
But what if I disappear?

789
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:35,700
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

790
00:38:35,730 --> 00:38:40,000
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

791
00:38:40,430 --> 00:38:42,840
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

792
00:38:42,990 --> 00:38:47,600
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

793
00:38:47,940 --> 00:38:51,900
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

794
00:38:51,930 --> 00:38:55,980
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

795
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,320
No matter where you are,

796
00:38:56,810 --> 00:39:01,120
♪ Together, forever ♪

797
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:01,080
I'll always find you.

798
00:39:22,420 --> 00:39:23,450
[Dynasty in turmoil again: Du Chengrong,
head of the Du family, bizarrely drowns]

799
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:27,130
[Chairman of Chengrong Group,
Du Chengrong]

800
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:33,720
Alright.

801
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:35,520
Let's eat.

802
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:37,720
This man Du Chengrong...

803
00:39:40,190 --> 00:39:41,400
I heard from Xiaolan

804
00:39:41,670 --> 00:39:43,550
there was a fight within the Du family.

805
00:39:43,550 --> 00:39:44,110
Du Chengrong's second son

806
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:45,910
has been missing for a long time.

807
00:39:46,110 --> 00:39:47,670
Given the Du family's background,

808
00:39:47,670 --> 00:39:49,320
it's no surprise for such a thing

809
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:49,960
to happen.

810
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:52,660
Look what it says here.

811
00:39:53,150 --> 00:39:55,010
Du Chengrong got into an accident

812
00:39:55,150 --> 00:39:57,350
on the way to negotiate an antique deal.

813
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:59,480
Granny Yu's son happens to do

814
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,140
antique business in Gangdao.

815
00:40:01,550 --> 00:40:02,800
When Xiaolan was there last time,

816
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:04,260
she had a meeting with him.

817
00:40:05,560 --> 00:40:06,360
For unknown reasons,

818
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,160
he just wouldn't come back here.

819
00:40:08,200 --> 00:40:09,600
I just don't understand.

820
00:40:09,670 --> 00:40:11,190
He hasn't seen his own mother

821
00:40:11,190 --> 00:40:12,190
for several decades.

822
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:14,590
How could he have the heart
not to come back?

823
00:40:15,030 --> 00:40:15,770
People...

824
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:18,080
find it the hardest to face themselves.

825
00:40:18,630 --> 00:40:19,400
Everything else

826
00:40:19,400 --> 00:40:20,400
is just an excuse.

827
00:40:21,110 --> 00:40:22,190
Do you mean deep down,

828
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:23,990
he's still clinging to the past?

829
00:40:24,500 --> 00:40:26,000
Xiaolan informed him

830
00:40:26,030 --> 00:40:27,320
of Granny Yu's sickness

831
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,440
and asked him to come back.

832
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,640
But he just wouldn't.

833
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:30,590
He said...

834
00:40:31,350 --> 00:40:32,880
he couldn't face Granny Yu.

835
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:34,960
Does it mean if he can never

836
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:36,250
move on from the past,

837
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,940
he won't see his mother again?

838
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:41,470
Granny Yu doesn't say anything,

839
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:42,400
but she surely misses

840
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,260
her son, right?

841
00:40:43,590 --> 00:40:44,650
What can we do then?

842
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,360
Nothing anyone says will help

843
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,960
if he can't get over the past.

844
00:40:48,190 --> 00:40:49,230
All we can do is spend

845
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:50,630
more time with Granny Yu.

846
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,030
Granny Yu will be discharged today.

847
00:40:52,030 --> 00:40:53,760
I'll stay at her place tonight.

848
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,670
So I'll have to be home alone?

849
00:40:55,670 --> 00:40:57,530
Just stay put and watch the house.

850
00:40:58,190 --> 00:40:58,840
When you bring

851
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,840
the old lady home, make sure

852
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,170
she gets plenty of rest.

853
00:41:01,710 --> 00:41:02,190
Thanks.

854
00:41:03,150 --> 00:41:04,840
I must make you chicken soup back home.

855
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,240
You need it for recovery.

856
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:23,640
What is he doing here?

857
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:24,440
Who?

858
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:27,140
Xu Zhongyi's assistant, Chai Hai.

859
00:41:27,140 --> 00:41:28,470
You go pick up Granny Yu.

860
00:41:29,590 --> 00:41:30,030
Okay.

861
00:41:34,190 --> 00:41:34,720
Chai Hai.

862
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:39,420
Before you disturb Granny Yu,

863
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,410
talk to me first.

864
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:42,360
Okay.

865
00:41:42,750 --> 00:41:46,660
[Shengcheng Municiple People's Hospital]

866
00:41:45,960 --> 00:41:46,490
Chai Hai,

867
00:41:47,030 --> 00:41:48,400
I remember asking Xu Zhongyi

868
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,800
to come to Shengcheng.

869
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:51,000
His mother

870
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,070
fell seriously ill.

871
00:41:52,070 --> 00:41:53,870
Isn't she worth a visit from him?

872
00:41:54,550 --> 00:41:55,150
Ms. Xia,

873
00:41:55,530 --> 00:41:56,930
Mr. Xu would love to come,

874
00:41:57,230 --> 00:41:58,880
but he's been swamped lately.

875
00:41:58,880 --> 00:42:00,550
He just went abroad last week
to pick up goods.

876
00:42:00,550 --> 00:42:01,280
It's not certain yet

877
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,340
when he'll be back.

878
00:42:02,710 --> 00:42:03,800
Xu Zhongyi...

879
00:42:04,400 --> 00:42:06,400
can afford a plane ticket, can't he?

880
00:42:07,150 --> 00:42:07,960
Mr. Xu said

881
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:09,070
he'd surely find time

882
00:42:09,070 --> 00:42:11,200
to visit Shengcheng when he came back.

883
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:12,710
This... is what he had me

884
00:42:12,710 --> 00:42:13,880
bring to his mother.

885
00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,230
Take it back.

886
00:42:16,190 --> 00:42:16,800
Also,

887
00:42:17,630 --> 00:42:19,360
pass a message to Mr. Qiu for me.

888
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:22,550
Tell him that during all these years
in Shengcheng,

889
00:42:22,550 --> 00:42:24,680
Granny Yu never needs stuff like this.

890
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:26,640
I'll take everything away,

891
00:42:27,230 --> 00:42:28,160
except for this.

892
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,200
Mr. Qiu told me

893
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:32,340
specifically to return this
to its original owner.

894
00:42:37,670 --> 00:42:38,800
Please do me a favor.

895
00:42:43,070 --> 00:42:43,960
Walk slowly.

896
00:42:44,230 --> 00:42:44,630
Okay.

897
00:42:45,480 --> 00:42:46,440
How do you feel?

898
00:42:47,070 --> 00:42:47,730
I feel fine.

899
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:48,170
Good.

900
00:42:49,510 --> 00:42:50,840
What are you doing here?

901
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:53,190
Wait here for a moment.

902
00:42:53,190 --> 00:42:53,800
I'll go get the car.

903
00:42:53,800 --> 00:42:54,130
Okay.

904
00:42:54,760 --> 00:42:56,230
Let's wait till he drives the car over

905
00:42:56,230 --> 00:42:57,290
before we head out.

906
00:42:59,110 --> 00:42:59,960
It's windy outside.

907
00:42:59,960 --> 00:43:01,290
Let's wait here for now.

908
00:43:01,480 --> 00:43:01,880
Okay.

909
00:43:02,710 --> 00:43:04,190
Let me fix your scarf.

910
00:43:08,280 --> 00:43:09,610
Granny Yu, you're back.

911
00:43:10,230 --> 00:43:10,690
Come on.

912
00:43:11,880 --> 00:43:12,480
Come here.

913
00:43:12,510 --> 00:43:14,230
How is it
that an old lady like me receives

914
00:43:14,230 --> 00:43:15,230
such a special treatment today?

915
00:43:15,230 --> 00:43:15,670
Look.

916
00:43:17,590 --> 00:43:18,720
If you like the food,

917
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:20,480
I'll cook for your every day.

918
00:43:20,480 --> 00:43:21,230
It's true

919
00:43:21,880 --> 00:43:22,960
that I've always wondered

920
00:43:22,960 --> 00:43:24,400
what Fen's daily diet

921
00:43:24,400 --> 00:43:25,110
is like.

922
00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:26,330
It's wonderful.

923
00:43:26,360 --> 00:43:27,110
I've even gained weight.

924
00:43:27,110 --> 00:43:27,630
Really?

925
00:43:27,690 --> 00:43:28,710
Going on a diet is a trend now.

926
00:43:28,710 --> 00:43:30,630
But Fen is not fat at all. She's so slim.

927
00:43:30,630 --> 00:43:32,280
There is a soup and two dishes coming.

928
00:43:32,280 --> 00:43:33,470
Rest for a bit, Granny Yu.

929
00:43:33,470 --> 00:43:34,480
Everyone, take a seat.

930
00:43:34,480 --> 00:43:36,140
I'll get you inside for a rest.

931
00:43:37,320 --> 00:43:38,180
Do you think...

932
00:43:38,360 --> 00:43:39,690
Xu Zhongyi saw all that?

933
00:43:40,360 --> 00:43:41,090
I don't know.

934
00:43:41,590 --> 00:43:42,230
But I think

935
00:43:42,800 --> 00:43:43,480
he must be around.
